  AUTHOR = {Massé, Cécile and Viard, Frédérique and Humbert, Suzie and Antajan, Elvire and Auby, Isabelle and Bachelet, Guy and Bernard, Guillaume and Bouchet, Vincent M. P. and Burel, Thomas and Dauvin, Jean-Claude and Delegrange, Alice and Derrien-Courtel, Sandrine and Droual, Gabin and Gouillieux, Benoit and Goulletquer, Philippe and Guérin, Laurent and Janson, Anne-Laure and Jourde, Jérôme and Labrune, Céline and Lavesque, Nicolas and Leclerc, Jean-Charles and Le Duff, Michel and Le Garrec, Vincent and Noël, Pierre and Nowaczyk, Antoine and Pergent-Martini, Christine and Pezy, Jean-Philippe and Raoux, Aurore and Raybaud, Virginie and Ruitton, Sandrine and Sauriau, Pierre-Guy and Spilmont, Nicolas and Thibault, Delphine and Vincent, Dorothée and Curd, Amelia},
